{"tid":1380411,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BigHit宣布收購GFRIEND公司！","createTime":"2019-07-29T04:17:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T05:59:13.000Z","uid":74065,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2fa6bbd67fa6738fc1e0d1301e778c6e43b667f5","tid":1380411,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:17:30.000Z","msg":"世界知名韓團防彈少年團（BTS）所屬公司BigHit娛樂29日宣布驚人消息，他們買下了在KPOP界擁有一席地位的女團GFRIEND所屬公司SOURCE MUSIC，而這還不是終點，未來還會再持續擴展，這也讓韓媒大膽表示：「三大經紀公司地位恐動搖。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4268/d4268200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4268%2Fd4268200.jpg&h=a28e3a6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲防彈少年團公司大動作收購經紀公司。（圖／翻攝自防彈少年團臉書）<br />\n<br />\nBigHit娛樂29日宣布已經完成收購SOURCE MUSIC股份合約，確定將之編入BigHit子公司中，這則新聞一出也讓「SOURCE MUSIC」和他們旗下女團「GFRIEND」登上NAVER熱搜，不只粉絲討論就連一般網友也對此話題展現高度興趣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4268/4268207.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4268%2F4268207.jpg&h=748e5173&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「SOURCE MUSIC」、「GFRIEND」、「BigHit」登NAVER熱搜。（圖／翻攝自NAVER）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">房時爀對外表示：「SOURCE MUSIC原有經營團隊都會留任，同時也將維持自己的獨立性和色彩，BigHit和SOURCE MUSIC對藝人培養和教育哲學的想法相似，對彼此也都很了解，我們都很期待這次收購會帶來成功，很高興雙方都能夠繪製更大的藍圖。」</span><br />\n<br />\nSOURCE MUSIC公司代表蘇成鎮則說：「很高興能和BigHit合作，我認為這對旗下藝人和練習生等所有人都是一個飛躍進步的機會，特別是BigHit在短時間內就打造出國際知名巨星，期待這份力量成為SOURCE MUSIC堅強後盾，和BigHit聯手後將以更好的Contents回報粉絲。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4268/d4268211.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4268%2Fd4268211.jpg&h=795f2eb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲GFRIEND所屬於SOURCE MUSIC。（圖／翻攝自GFRIEND臉書）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">另外，據韓媒《TVREPORT》報導，BigHit娛樂計畫將再收購另一個擁有高人氣男團的經紀公司，目前雙方合約仍有需要調整事項，因此還沒有正式公布，但業界人士透露其實這項收購合併案幾乎已成定局，最晚在2020年就會確定了。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n至此，幾乎百分百收入來源都靠防彈少年團的BigHit，目前已經確定收購擁有GFRIEND和受訓系統完善的女練習生，若再加上男團經紀公司整個版圖會更加堅固。他們的藍圖不只偶像領域，還有人氣TROT歌手經紀公司也在討論中，該公司相關人士29日透露：「目前還沒有具體事項。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，BigHit明年將搬入的新大樓擁有地上19層、地下7層，被收購的SOURCE MUSIC人員們也都將一起搬入。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wjrIXNbkwd0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwjrIXNbkwd0&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67ZIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=a8ed00b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wjrIXNbkwd0</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/4cXA5mm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F4cXA5mm.jpg&h=d7ce4d2d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51fac2af3b9de05974525681dc213e62bfb98587","tid":1380411,"uid":2781,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:30:58.000Z","msg":"唔覺得係好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38fd02ad5592f40f4939b1cb4a77a073e8974d8f","tid":1380411,"uid":68678,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:31:11.000Z","msg":"sinb 同銀河 (?) 兜兜轉轉最尾都番番bighit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6065a95e59734afdc897c8717f4732dfec3cc6d5","tid":1380411,"uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"51fac2af3b9de05974525681dc213e62bfb98587","tid":1380411,"uid":2781,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:30:58.000Z","msg":"唔覺得係好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:32:14.000Z","msg":"唔係好識但就咁睇有咩壞處<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"657630aa330fcc3fe20d21e135fe69d7b7c63498","tid":1380411,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:32:54.000Z","msg":"See you in~~Wednesday ~~"},{"pid":"aea3bbaab70014b5f89e10c4ed4f880e6de595de","tid":1380411,"uid":3189,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:33:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.